org.aksw.iguana.rp.storage.impl

Class PropertiesSenderStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aksw.iguana.rp.storage.SenderStorage<java.util.Properties>
      • org.aksw.iguana.rp.storage.impl.PropertiesSenderStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Storage

    public class PropertiesSenderStorage
extends SenderStorage<java.util.Properties>
    Will provide all the results as Properties and will send them to a rabbit queue
    The rabbit queue can be defined by the constructor. The default name is "rp2PropertiesSender"

    The Triples will be converted to: {predicate(key):object(value)}
    Author:
    f.conrads
